## Example
#### Call

    https://apigateway.serpro.gov.br/consulta-nfe-df-trial/api/v1/nfe/push/clientes



#### URL Terminations

    Customer monitoring requests will only be notified if the registered URLs end with .br or .com. See the examples:                                              https://url_cliente.com                                                                   https://url_cliente.br 

#### Input content
    { 
      "urlNotificacao": "https://url_cliente.com" 
    }

                      or 

    { 
      "urlNotificacao": "https://url_cliente.br" 
    } 
  #### Return
    { 
      "Id": "000000000000000", 
      "urlNotificacao": "https://url_cliente.com", 
      "dataCriacao": "2019-12-20T03:00:00.000Z" 
    } 

                      or 

    { 
      "Id": "000000000000000", 
      "urlNotificacao": "https://url_cliente.br", 
      "dataCriacao": "2019-12-20T03:00:00.000Z" 
    }

